  <h3 class="text-gray-500 text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-light">
    and I'm fluent in 
    <span class="text-red-500 font-normal">Ruby</span>, 
    <span class="text-yellow-500 font-normal">HTML</span>,
    <span class="text-blue-400 font-normal">CSS</span>, 
